h1_title: Best Settings on PS5 and PC
content: While you should also consider the High settings start by trying Very High in this category if you still have some overhead as visually, it’s almost the exact same as the Cinematic option. High, Medium, and Low will introduce some issues, but continue giving noticeable bumps in performance
